reviews.review_text: rock on we will love forever through your work.please don't stop!!!! Mike Blanks

The Dome This show was awesome. End of the Summer Tour 88 was an amazing time, the Grateful Dead rarely played the Seattle area. The scene was completely thriving and the vibes were simmering with positive energy.
